Executive Profile
Peter D. Ley  Chief Financial Officer, Capitol Infrastructure, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships57--
Background

		Mr. Peter D. Ley served as the Chief Financial Officer of Hargray Communications Group, Inc until October 5, 2015. Mr. Ley is responsible for accounting and financial controls, treasury, insurance, lender relations and financial planning and analysis. He has experience as a Chief Financial Officer and Board member at innovative and high-growth businesses in the communications industry. His career also includes a broad background in strategic finance as an investment ... banker to the technology, communications and related sectors. Prior to joining Hargray, he served as the Chief Financial Officer of Capitol Infrastructure, LLC (alternate name Connexion Technologies). Mr. Ley is a telecommunications, financial management and investment banking expertise. He served as Managing Director of Investment Banking at Bank of America Securities for seven years. He was responsible for managing client relationships with the U.S. telecom industry. He served as the Chief Financial Officer of Pennsylvania-based Commonwealth Telephone Enterprises LLC. He has been an Independent Director of Alaska Communications Systems Group Inc. since August 1, 2008. Mr. Ley holds a B.A. in Economics and Government from Dartmouth College and an M.B.A from Harvard University.Read Full Background




