Insider Activity


Individual




Peter D. Ley



Mr. Peter D. Ley is Chief Financial Officer at Hargray Holdings LLC and Independent Director at Alaska Communications Systems Group, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Alaska Communications Systems Group, Inc.
Mr. Ley was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer by Capitol Infrastructure LLC, Chief Financial Officer by Commonwealth Telephone Enterprises, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Hargray Communications Group, Inc., and Senior Media & Telecom Investment Banker by Banc of America Securities LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from Dartmouth College and an MBA from Harvard University.



